                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On September 14, the Foreign Ministers of France, the United Kingdom, and the
                    United States, meeting in Washington, issued a statement in support of European
                    unity. For text of this statement, see <ref target="frus1951v03p1#pg_1306"
                        >volume III, Part 1, page 1306</ref>.</p>
